#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:4
msgid "简介：用于对两个张量进行逐元素逻辑与运算"
msgstr "Introduction: Used to perform element-wise logical AND operation on two tensors."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"x.logical_and(y)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:8
msgid "作为`tensor`的成员函数调用, 如`x0.logical_and(x1)`。"
msgstr "Called as a member function of `tensor`, e.g., `x0.logical_and(x1)`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:10
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:12
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:14
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | 张量数据, 左操作数, 代表要进行比较的主数据 |\n"
"| `other`   | `tensor` | 张量数据, 右操作数, 与`input`逐元素进行逻辑与 |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"| :---: | :---: | :---: |\n"
"| `input` | `tensor` | Tensor data, left operand, representing the primary data to be compared |\n"
"| `other` | `tensor` | Tensor data, right operand, performs element-wise logical AND with `input` |\n"
"| `_builder` | - | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:16
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tl.tensor`：同`input`的shape的张量\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tl.tensor`: A tensor with the same shape as `input`.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Logical_Ops/logical_and.md:18
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

